&lt;h3 id=&#34;select-courses100pt&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#select-courses100pt&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Select Courses(100pt)&lt;/h3&gt;
