&lt;h2 id=&#34;nisactf-2022shop_pwn&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#nisactf-2022shop_pwn&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; [NISACTF 2022]shop_pwn&lt;/h2&gt;
